    "On launch, KeiPix asks GitHub for the latest release once per 24-hour window, compares it to the running CFBundleShortVersionString, and surfaces a banner with Open Release Notes / Skip / Later actions when a newer tag is published.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "On launch, KeiPix asks GitHub for the latest release once per 24-hour window, compares it to the running CFBundleShortVersionString, and surfaces a banner with Open Release Notes / Skip / Later actions when a newer tag is published."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "起動時、KeiPix は 24 時間に 1 回 GitHub から最新リリースを取得し、稼働中の CFBundleShortVersionString と比較します。新しいタグが公開されている場合は「リリースノートを開く / スキップ / 後で」のバナーを表示します。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "启动时，KeiPix 每 24 小时向 GitHub 查询一次最新版本，与运行中的 CFBundleShortVersionString 对比，发现新版本时弹出包含「打开发行说明 / 跳过 / 稍后」操作的提示。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "啟動時，KeiPix 每 24 小時向 GitHub 查询一次最新版本，與運行中的 CFBundleShortVersionString 對比，發現新版本時弹出包含「開啟發行說明 / 跳過 / 稍後」操作的提示。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Once a day, KeiPix asks GitHub whether a newer release has been published. Disable this to skip the check entirely.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Once a day, KeiPix asks GitHub whether a newer release has been published. Disable this to skip the check entirely."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "KeiPix は 1 日 1 回 GitHub に新しいリリースを問い合わせます。確認自体を行いたくない場合はオフにしてください。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "KeiPix 每天会向 GitHub 查询一次是否发布了新版本。关闭此项即可完全跳过检查。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "KeiPix 每天會向 GitHub 查询一次是否發佈了新版本。關閉此項即可完全跳過檢查。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
