    "Routes Pixiv API and image traffic through the chosen proxy. \"Follow System\" honours macOS network settings; manual mode and direct mode take effect after relaunching KeiPix.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Routes Pixiv API and image traffic through the chosen proxy. \"Follow System\" honours macOS network settings; manual mode and direct mode take effect after relaunching KeiPix."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pixiv API と画像通信を選択したプロキシ経由で送ります。「システムに従う」は macOS のネットワーク設定を尊重します。手動モードと直接接続モードは KeiPix の再起動後に反映されます。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "通过所选代理转发 Pixiv API 和图片流量。「跟随系统」会沿用 macOS 网络设置；「手动」与「直连」需重新启动 KeiPix 后生效。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "通過所選代理轉發 Pixiv API 和圖片流量。「跟随系統」會沿用 macOS 網路設定；「手動」與「直連」需重新啟動 KeiPix 後生效。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
