            "value": "This copies a long-lived Pixiv credential. Only paste it into KeiPix on a device you control."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "長期有効な Pixiv 認証情報をコピーします。自分が管理するデバイスの KeiPix にだけ貼り付けてください。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这会复制一个长期有效的 Pixiv 凭据。只粘贴到你自己设备上的 KeiPix。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "這會複製一個長期有效的 Pixiv 憑證。只貼到你自己裝置上的 KeiPix。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This feed is restored from the last successful load and stays read-only until refresh succeeds.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "This feed is restored from the last successful load and stays read-only until refresh succeeds."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "このフィードは最後に成功した読み込みから復元され、更新が成功するまで読み取り専用"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "当前作品流来自上次成功载入的缓存；刷新成功前保持只读浏览。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "當前作品流來自上次成功載入的快取；刷新成功前保持只讀瀏覽。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This imports muted tags and creators from your Pixiv account into this Mac. You can undo the local changes after syncing.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "This imports muted tags and creators from your Pixiv account into this Mac. You can undo the local changes after syncing."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "PixivアカウントからミュートタグとクリエイターをこのMacにインポートします。同期後にローカル変更を元に戻せます"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这会把 Pixiv 账号里的屏蔽标签和创作者导入到这台 Mac。同步后的本地改动可以撤销。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "這會把 Pixiv 帳號裡的封鎖標籤和創作者導入到這台 Mac。同步後的本地改動可以復原。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This replaces local muted content with the selected file. You can undo the local changes after importing.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "This replaces local muted content with the selected file. You can undo the local changes after importing."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ローカルのミュートコンテンツを選択したファイルで置き換えます。インポート後にローカル変更を元に戻せます"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这会用所选文件替换本地屏蔽内容。导入后的本地改动可以撤销。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "這會用所選檔案替換本地封鎖內容。導入後的本地改動可以復原。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
