    "KeiPix can rebuild every cache below from Pixiv on demand. Clearing one frees space; clearing all reverts the app to a clean install state without touching your bookmarks, downloads, or muted lists.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "KeiPix can rebuild every cache below from Pixiv on demand. Clearing one frees space; clearing all reverts the app to a clean install state without touching your bookmarks, downloads, or muted lists."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "以下のキャッシュはすべて Pixiv から再構築できます。個別に消すと容量が空き、全消去するとブックマーク・ダウンロード・ミュートには影響せずクリーンな状態に戻せます。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "以下所有缓存都可以从 Pixiv 重新拉取。逐项清理可释放空间；一键清空会让应用回到干净状态，但不会影响收藏、下载和屏蔽列表。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "以下所有快取都能從 Pixiv 重新取得。逐項清理可釋放空間；全部清除會讓 App 回到乾淨狀態，但不會影響書籤、下載與封鎖名單。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
